         adduser,
         openssl,
         systemd (>= 235),
Suggests: sssd-dbus,
         python3,
Description: Buddy Web Service
 The Buddy Web Service listens on the network, and authenticates
 users.
 .
 Install sssd-dbus for supporting client certificate/smart card authentication
 via sssd/FreeIPA.

